search_results.title: Snowdrop (South Korean TV series)
search_results.snippet: Snowdrop is a South Korean television series starring Jung Hae-in, Jisoo, Yoo In-na, Jang Seung-jo, Yoon Se-ah, Kim Hye-yoon and Jung Yoo-jin.

search_results.title: Snowdrop, Harland
search_results.snippet: Harland explores a variety of cultural meanings for the deceptively petit flower. In Victorian England snowdrop bands encouraged chastity among young women.
